After Shino releases a swarm of [[kidaichū]], Kiba transforms into the [[Human Beast Mixture Transformation — Three-Headed Wolf|three-headed wolf]] and [[Tail Chasing Fang Fang Rotating Fang|rapidly spins]] towards the enemy along with Shino's bugs. Hinata then jumps into the spinning vortex and uses her [[Byakugan]] to lodge the bugs onto the opponent's tenketsu. As the opponent is thrown back, Shino's kidaichū grow rapidly, eating them from the inside out.
